refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public static QuickHashIntStringHashQuickHashIntStringHash::loadFromString stringcontents intsize0 intoptions0
Cette méthode d'usine crée un nouveau hachage à partir d'une définition dans une chaîne. Le format est le même que celui utilisé dans "loadFromFile".

&reftitle.examples;
Exemple de QuickHashIntStringHash::loadFromString
<?php $contents = file_get_contents( dirname( __FILE__ ) . "/simple.hash" ); $hash = QuickHashIntStringHash::loadFromString( $contents, QuickHashIntStringHash::DO_NOT_USE_ZEND_ALLOC ); foreach( range( 0, 0x0f ) as $key ) { printf( "Key %3d (%2x) is %s\n", $key, $key, $hash->exists( $key ) ? 'set' : 'unset' ); } ?>
&example.outputs.similar;
Key 0 ( 0) is unset Key 1 ( 1) is set Key 2 ( 2) is set Key 3 ( 3) is set Key 4 ( 4) is unset Key 5 ( 5) is set Key 6 ( 6) is unset Key 7 ( 7) is set Key 8 ( 8) is unset Key 9 ( 9) is unset Key 10 ( a) is unset Key 11 ( b) is set Key 12 ( c) is unset Key 13 ( d) is set Key 14 ( e) is unset Key 15 ( f) is unset
